4 classes created Phone, Apple, Samsung, Main

Make Phone a super class.

Create static String arraylist name is "cart"

create method name is getSum
One String as a parameter
and return type is int
        get the String remove all non numeric letters or special characters
        then change String to int
        Return the Num

create one abstract method name is options
parameter is two Strings
return type is String


in the Apple class
    extends the Phone class
override the options method
     there are 2 strings as a parameter
     return type is String

   if String one is 64 GB and 5.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$750"

   if String one is 64 GB and 6.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$850"

   if String one is 128 GB and 5.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$950"

   if String one is 128 GB and 6.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$1200"


in the Samsung class
  extends the Phone class
override the options method
     there are 2 strings as a parameter
     return type is String

   if String one is 256 GB and 5.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$1000"

   if String one is 256 GB and 7.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$1200"

   if String one is 512 GB and 5.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$1300"

   if String one is 512 GB and 6.5 inch
        add in the cart arraylist  "$1400"

in the Main class
    create scanner class object
       create four Strings str1 , str2 , str3 , str4 and assign scanner object to Strings

Create object for apple class
call the options method in apple class
     options parameters are str1 , str2


Create object for samsung class
call the options method in samsung class
